OL,3,CSentencing of mum for 1998 killing of
OL,4,Cbaby delayed
OL,6,FThe sentencing of a mum who admitted
OL,7,Fkilling her newborn son 25 years ago
OL,8,Fhas been delayed after the judge said
OL,9,Fshe needed time to 'reflect' on the
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FThe baby boy was given the name Callum
OL,13,Fafter his body was found by a dog
OL,14,Fwalker in woods near the Gulliver's
OL,15,FWorld theme park in Warrington on 14
OL,16,FMarch 1998.
