OL,3,CSentencing of mum for 1998 killing of
OL,4,Cbaby delayed
OL,6,FMum Joanne Sharkey, 55, from Croxteth,
OL,7,FLiverpool, was finally identified in
OL,8,F2023 when cold case detectives found a
OL,9,Fmatch for her older son in national
OL,10,FDNA databases.
OL,12,FSharkey was arrested and charged in
OL,13,FApril 2024 with murdering the child,
OL,14,Fwho was believed to be hours old at
OL,15,Fthe time of his death, and concealing
OL,16,Fthe birth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
