OL,3,CSentencing of mum for 1998 killing of
OL,4,Cbaby delayed
OL,6,FShe admitted manslaughter on the basis
OL,7,Fof diminished responsibility, as well
OL,8,Fas concealing the birth of a child, on
OL,9,Fthe first day of her trial at
OL,10,FLiverpool Crown Court.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Service accepted
OL,13,Fthe plea after it was found Sharkey
OL,14,Fhad been suffering from a "moderate to
OL,15,Fsevere depressive illness" which
OL,16,F"substantially impaired her ability to
OL,17,Fform rational judgement and exercise
OL,18,Fself control".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
