OL,3,CSentencing of mum for 1998 killing of
OL,4,Cbaby delayed
OL,6,FThe judge at Liverpool Crown Court,
OL,7,FMrs Justice Eady, said: "This is a
OL,8,Fcase where I need to reflect and think
OL,9,Fabout very carefully what is the
OL,10,Fappropriate course.
OL,12,F"While I appreciate the stress
OL,13,Finvolved in putting sentence off to
OL,14,Fanother date, I'm afraid that is where
OL,15,FI think we are."JSentencing will now
OL,16,Ftake place on 4 April.
OL,18,FThe judge told Sharkey: "This is a
OL,19,Fcase where I need to reflect on what I
OL,20,Fhave heard. I am not in a position to
OL,21,Fgo on to pass sentence this afternoon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
