OL,3,CSentencing of mum for 1998 killing of
OL,4,Cbaby delayed
OL,6,F"I appreciate the stress that causes
OL,7,Fyou and family members. I am sorry
OL,8,Fabout that but it is more important if
OL,9,FI make sure I make the right decision
OL,10,Frather than trying to rush things on a
OL,11,FFriday afternoon."
OL,13,FNina Grahame KC, defending Sharkey,
OL,14,Ftold the court: "She never denied that
OL,15,Fthe baby had been born alive. She
OL,16,Fsimply didn't know. Given she didn't
OL,17,Fknow, it's right to say the
OL,18,Fpathologists didn't know. They
OL,19,Fcouldn't reach a conclusion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
