OL,6,F"Mrs Sharkey has of course been
OL,7,Fimpacted in terms of her mental health
OL,8,Fby these proceedings. We don't suggest
OL,9,Fthe type of condition she was
OL,10,Fsuffering at the time has continued
OL,11,Funtil now.
OL,13,F"But the impact of these proceedings
OL,14,Fhas been enormous. That has impacted
OL,15,Fon the ability to advise and take
OL,16,Finstructions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
