OL,6,F"Those admissions in interview are, we
OL,7,Fsuggest, a powerful and important
OL,8,Ffeature of mitigation in this case,
OL,9,Fnot easy and taking a great deal of
OL,10,Fcourage. She made them in fact before
OL,11,Fshe was even interviewed."
